imdb.plot outline: We all have a story to tell, we all have a destiny to realize, and FAN MOGULS seeks to help three talented fans achieve theirs! Fan Moguls takes the audience on a journey to fan conventions across the country, while helping three talented fans on the path to achieving their professional dreams, challenging them to earn the training they need by hunting down the most compelling fan stories around the country.
imdb.title: Fan Moguls
plot: Three contestants travel to fan conventions across the country, seeking out the best stories of each fandom while competing to earn the training they need to realize their destiny.::V.C.

We all have a story to tell, we all have a destiny to realize, and FAN MOGULS seeks to help three talented fans achieve theirs! _Fan Moguls_ (qv) takes the audience on a journey to fan conventions across the country, while helping three talented fans on the path to achieving their professional dreams, challenging them to earn the training they need by hunting down the most compelling fan stories around the country.::Zak Vaudo
